# Yomitan Character Dictionary Builder — Complete Implementation Plan

**Project:** Standalone Website for Generating Yomitan Character Dictionaries  
**Architecture:** Rust (Axum) Server + Simple HTML/CSS/JS Frontend  
**Status:** Implementation ready — all APIs, data models, and algorithms documented with complete code

---

## TABLE OF CONTENTS

1. Project Overview
2. Architecture & File Structure
3. Complete Cargo.toml
4. Shared Data Model (models.rs)
5. VNDB API Client Implementation
6. AniList API Client Implementation
7. Name Parser Module (Japanese name handling)
8. Content Builder Module (Yomitan structured content)
